\boxed{D. Disclosing the most important information so that it can be understood as fully as possible}

This approach respects the parents' need for immediate understanding and supports them in processing the information at their own pace, rather than overwhelming them with details that may not be immediately relevant. It also sets the stage for further discussions and decisions that will be made in the future.

